    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mazey Village Demo 🌿</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tornado has scattered belongings and broken homes across a once-peaceful town. In this <strong>demo</strong>, step into the role of a maze navigator and get a first taste of exploring, recovering lost items, and rebuilding the village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/a72385c28ba7056a7745b516068f903d.poster.avif?t=1758722860\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/a72385c28ba7056a7745b516068f903d.webm?t=1758722860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the Meadows ✨</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the first maze region and uncover hidden paths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for belongings scattered across the maze world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet cozy creatures and playful interactables waiting to surprise you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/03f6c08cccda9a35c2f7bb3f9c6e4a88.poster.avif?t=1758722860\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/03f6c08cccda9a35c2f7bb3f9c6e4a88.webm?t=1758722860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rebuild and Customize the Village 🏡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design the town your way by placing decorations, shaping its layout, and creating a cozy space that matches your style. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore homes and welcome villagers back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate with furniture, gardens, and charming details.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the village flourish as you bring the community together!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/739ddfc55b9f37e84f8dad09f621b4fb.poster.avif?t=1758722860\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/739ddfc55b9f37e84f8dad09f621b4fb.webm?t=1758722860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World Full of Life 🐮</strong> <br><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From petting cows and penguins to uncovering hidden stories, <strong>Mazey Village</strong> is full of little moments that make every step special.<br><br>✨<strong>The demo offers a small taste of the cozy adventures waiting in the full game.<br></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/319ff4fc1d72537425934aae1064ae3b.poster.avif?t=1758722860\" width=800 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865910/extras/319ff4fc1d72537425934aae1064ae3b.webm?t=1758722860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p>",
